Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:34.46,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:23.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:24.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:39.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As of today, I've been reassigned to Events Department 3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:40.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's my 2nd year working here, my name is Takagi Shinji
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:42.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:44.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's unusual to be reassigned at this time of year
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A rookie...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:47.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,2nd year...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:48.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Weren't you in department 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:50.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right, I came from Events Department 1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:51.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Getting reassigned from department 1 to 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:53.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:53.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:54.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it "Se" or "Po"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:56.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Pro Baseball League?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:57.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Sexual harassment or Power harassment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:00:58.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Or is it "Re"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:00:59.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Remote harassment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:01.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My first ever junior
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:06.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, can I have your attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:07.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:10.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I found four areas for improvement in this department just by taking a quick glance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:11.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:12.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The first one is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:15.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,it's inefficient to manually put all of these flyers into an envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:19.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's better to just outsource this and use your time to get more projects instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:20.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a more effective use of your time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:23.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is to show our sincerity towards Manten Nodoame-san
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.61,0:01:25.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is the second improvement point
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:28.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,80% of this department's sales is from Manten Nodoame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:31.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that it's dangerous to just rely on one big client?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:33.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's so unpleasant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The third point...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well well
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:36.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's take it easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:38.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:40.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best as a team
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:47.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't think that I can deal with him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:50.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because he's my junior, I can ask him to make copies of documents, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:51.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Listen up everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:52.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:54.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's with this atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:55.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:58.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've been reassigned from Department 1, my name is Takagi Shinji
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:01:59.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Takagi Shinji-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:00.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji it is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:02.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Meet you-nice to, Shinji
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:04.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've found the fifth area for improvement
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:04.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Improvement?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you have something to say, Inuzuka-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:09.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right Kijimura-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:10.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Listen up everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:15.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Department 3 is now in charge of a sports car PR event
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:16.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that the project is too big? Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Department 1 can't handle it, so it was passed down to us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There it is, the customary hand-me-down work for Department 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,When is the presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:25.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In 3 days
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:26.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's over the speed limit for Department 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:31.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Everyone, would you like to go full throttle with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:33.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:36.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Making copies of the presentation documents should be done by my junior Shinji-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:37.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:39.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's still a long ways off, Komukai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:48.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Sports car is a fashion item for men
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:49.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Having a cute girl on the passenger seat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and then cutting trough the wind in Shonan beach
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:57.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Men will shine when riding a sports car
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, Kijimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:03:58.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But don't you think that it's a bit old fashioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:05.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A sports car should be like going through a pass at high speed and then drifts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That sounds cool
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,People call me the explosive kid from Nerima
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're a racer, Saruwatari?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:10.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Intial D
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're talking about an arcade in Nerima then
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:17.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that we should proceed based on facts, not by vague impressions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Facts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is the target demographic for the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that it's working people in their 40's and under
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's me and Nakano-san
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:27.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:32.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The point is how to bring sports car closer to young people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right, that is what we want
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:37.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Or how to bring young people closer to sports car
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:42.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that it's better for just us, young people, to work on this presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:43.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at this data
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:49.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,More than 50% of people in their 20's said that they don't need a car
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:52.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The number is even higher when it comes to sports car
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The reason is that they don't want to stand out,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:55.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,they don't know when to drive it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,it's not a status symbol as it used to be, and so on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:01.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We can sympathize with these kind of answers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, just the three of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:07.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The truth is that I used to ride my Grandfather's Porsche
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:09.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your grandfather's Porsche...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:12.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The luxurious glossy seats and sunsets by the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was deeply moved as a child back then
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your grandfather's Porsche...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:21.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful memory, just like a gem
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:26.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that it's better to leave it to these young people over here, Kijimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:26.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:29.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Shinji
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:30.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go for it, all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait just a sec
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:34.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What did he meant by "Go for it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:41.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey you, are you dumb or are you smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the key to changing the perception of sports car
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:46.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,To that end, the ones who think about how to achieve it must be young as well
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He seems smart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Young people these days are very rational
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:56.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So we can win if we can show that value of owning a sports car outweighs the price and inconvenience
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:56.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:58.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It sounds like we're making progress, but we're actually not
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:01.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, the two of you, let's come up with a plan in this direction
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:02.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can we meet up again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:04.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course! What about you, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best until it's time to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No need to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:11.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about this again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm immediately tired because of him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:21.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that the capable vibes that he gives off in his 2nd year is amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:27.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hear me out, sports car is a dream of every man
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, another round on the rocks please
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:32.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't care about all of that, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What car did you drive back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nissan Silvia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was shining back then, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,now I drive a car with sliding doors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Sliding doors, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:45.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about before I know it, I'm riding a family car with sliding doors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I totally get it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Aren't you single, Saruwatari-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:51.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is the project going to be okay, Nakano?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:55.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, Shinji said that there's no need to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's not reassuring at all
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I guess that you guys will hold back if we're part of the team
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do what you want young'uns
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Say what's on your minds and get the project over the line
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:04.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're just scared of his grandfather's Porsche, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:08.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Tell you the truth, I was shaking after I heard him say that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's get started
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's finish making the presentation today
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:17.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:22.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:23.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:24.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No no no
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:25.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:26.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:27.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't say that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that you were going to come up with a plan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:33.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I said that let's come up with a plan in direction to the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why did you say "No need to worry" and "I'm here" then
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here right now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You meant that literally?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is there any other meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:44.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This person is crazy after all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:44.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if you're angry, nothing will come of it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:47.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Calm down
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko, it's better if we do this just the two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:53.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:54.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:55.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can go home now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:56.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:59.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I got some sharp insights from you, so it's all good, right Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's all good
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If everything is alright, then I'm going to leave it to the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:08.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Listen up, presentation is a battle of passion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The rareness of a sports car...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Stop talking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:15.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, please excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Having a presentation in 2 days is really tough
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A battle of passion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:26.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:29.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is presentation all about our passion, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That has got nothing to do with it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As long as we succeed, it doesn't matter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How much is a sports car anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:39.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:40.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,20 million
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:41.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,20 million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Who buys a sports car then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Either a rich person or a dreamer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why do people call it sports car?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:53.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Cars that was developed with an emphasis on the enjoyment of sports driving
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:56.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The explosive kid from Nerima
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That was an indoor arcade kid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:00.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:03.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Tell us, Google
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Projection mapping
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I missed the regular time to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:16.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,From now on, we're going to waste our time the most in our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Looks good
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's more like it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go with this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:27.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Leave the presentation to me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're the top runner in the not-passionate world, Nakano-san
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Who cares about passion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to buy some drinks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, let's go home by 18:30
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:43.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're still here, Komukai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ooishi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:47.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:49.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go home by 18:30
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that the sports car project?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:52.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:54.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So you're the one in charge of the project
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:57.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How do I say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There is nothing that appeals to me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:18.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Something that appeals to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:23.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the distance between you and the car
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:27.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you fallen for sports car?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:29.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:32.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that being in charge of the promotion means that conveying the charms of said product?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:37.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But you can only see the charms after you've fallen for it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:38.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You still have a lot of time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:41.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,as something that you came up with in a hurry, it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:43.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:49.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't came up with this in a hurry though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:55.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:58.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you love sports car, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:05.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, it looks like that we have to love it or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Or else? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:14.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can I go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:16.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is everthing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to see if I can properly love it or not
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:29.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good evening
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:32.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:33.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You want more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:35.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,More?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't it Zaku-Oneesan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for another plastic model?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it really unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Having someone come for more is a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:46.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is unthinkable for a young women customer to come here again for the second time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:50.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to look for something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:51.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Zaku-nee
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:52.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is the beginning of your plastic model journey
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:55.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Plastic model journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our side
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Found it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:23.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Zaku-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This looks like it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:37.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nissan R35 GT-R
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:41.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a 2014 model GT-R by Nissan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:45.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A gran turismo with a high quality and comfortable riding experience and the overwhelming speed of it's racing technology
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:49.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,With those two qualities, it's a dream car for adults who are after those two qualities
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:55.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a high end Japanese made sports car for those who continue to yearn for the glorious days of their youth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:56.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The price...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:00.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Around 10 million
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:01.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's 3,740 yen for the plastic model
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll buy it then
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,By the way, the body is centered on it's back side
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:08.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, Riko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's okay to buy it and then go home
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,or it's also okay to build it here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:15.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"Open the box"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to put your seat belt on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:23.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san, please go full throttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:24.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:27.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko is off
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:32.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Open the box
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:34.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:35.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:41.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's completely different from the Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:44.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The parts are too detailed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's packed with dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's actually a nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:48.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Giving up already, Zaku-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Sports cars are getting further and further away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:52.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:54.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,plastic models also teaches you how to overcome difficulties
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:00.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is for the tires
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:06.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,By placing a spring over there, it can realistically simulate the bouncy feeling of a real car
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:08.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The same as a real car
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:10.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Carefully cutting the parts out of the runner
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You will damage the parts itself if you're too aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:15.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Leave a bit of the gates on the parts, because you're going to smooth it out later
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's so small
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You missed one
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is the radiator hose, an important part of the car
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That was close
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:58.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So small
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you going to assemble it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:02.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:05.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because it's a sports car, I'm sure want to paint it to look cool
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:09.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's completely different from the Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:11.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Just this once...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:27.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So cool
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:30.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks real, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:32.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Just this once
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:34.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's so detailed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's where people sit on the car
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Put it on while thinking about who's going to sit on it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Who is on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ride it alone
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, imagine it's you then
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:16.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't have a driver's license
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:18.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Just put it on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:49.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:08.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't do it, it's too small
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:10.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Zaku-nee
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:13.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That part is the equivalent to a human's heart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:17.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The car won't move without it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:19.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? This plastic model can move?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:20.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:22.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why should I put it on then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's because it's the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:57.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So precious
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why did you paint it red?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because it's the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The engine looks better in silver
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:05.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:07.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can do anything with plastic models
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:30.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:44.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:48.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Once I put the body on, the engine is no longer visible
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:49.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:53.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not visible, even though it was hard to assemble it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We put our heart and soul into it, even into the invisible internal parts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is the great thing about this scale model
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:03.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The plastic model journey, I still have a long way to go
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It snapped on
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:32.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,GT-R, give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well done
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:37.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This feels so heavy for some reason
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:39.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because it's filled with dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:42.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You loved sports car, don't you Zaku-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:42.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was just looking for a reason to love it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:49.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,When you're looking for a reason, your love for it is already up and running
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I already love it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:58.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This time, we would like to propose the Five Senses Showroom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:04.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a PR event where people can actually experience interacting with parts of a dissembled sports car
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:09.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you count all the parts of a car down to the smallest screws, there are more than 30.000 parts in total
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:17.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Our goal is to bring young people and sports car closer by letting them interact with parts of the car that people don't really get to see
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:18.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:22.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,By the way, how did you come up with the idea for this project?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:25.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:33.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I build a plastic model of a sports car after I was entrusted with this project
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Plastic model?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:35.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:40.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for saying this, but at first I don't understand why would someone buy a sports cars
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:44.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's why I build it as something to get me to love it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:51.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:55.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,every single parts looked so cool
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I became gradually drawn into it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:07.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The beautiful internal parts, that is hard to imagine from the outside, is packed with a lot of parts and technologies
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:10.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that it's so precious
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:32.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If a 1/24th scale of a car can make me this excited,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:36.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,a real car would be even more exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:40.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is all for our presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:42.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:44.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:47.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,About the sports car event...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:52.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The client accepted it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:53.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:54.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good job
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:56.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:00.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Great job! Did you bribe them or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:01.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:07.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work Nakano-san, Riko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:08.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I read your proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:11.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You really took the concepts that I said to heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:12.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you, Shinji
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:13.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nothing less from the former Department 1 member
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:14.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:17.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But there are 5 areas that need improvement
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:17.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Improvement?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:20.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,First of all is the we didn't prepare a backup plan
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:23.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Normally we would prepare plan A, B and C...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:25.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I should give him a proper beat down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:26.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:28.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,